Merkel Wins ‘Very Clear’ Coalition Majority, CDU Whip Says

-- B y   P a t r i c k   D o n a h u e
-- 
2011-09-29T10:27:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-29/merkel-wins-very-clear-coalition-majority-cdu-whip-says.html
Chancellor  Angela Merkel  won a
“very clear” majority in her coalition for today’s approval of
the European bailout fund in the lower house of parliament,
according to  Peter Altmaier , the parliamentary whip in Merkel’s
 Christian Democratic Union .   “In the end, the unity of the coalition was stronger than
the dissent,” Altmaier told ZDF television today after the vote
in favor of the expanded European Financial Stability Facility.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Patrick Donahue at 
 pdonahue1@bloomberg.net  